<p><span style="font-family: 'Nothing You Could Do' ;"><span style="font-size:80%;">Eurtec is the beating heart of the Global Occult Coalition — <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/unfounded-hub" target="_blank">humanity's only resistance against the unknown</a>. Spanning hundreds of kilometers from the highest towers of the Golden District to the lowest depths of the Undercity, a heavy shadow falls over those caught between the oppression of the Coalition's cruel Enforcers and the paracrime of the Blood District.</span></span></p>
